description:
The new kitz/subpath-imports-integrity rule surfaced 12 missing-entry warnings across three packages. Need to add missing # subpath import entries to package.json for each, and let the tsconfig autofix handle the rest.

@kitz/core: mask, ref, value, num/allocation, str/char, str/nat, str/tpl, str/case
@kitz/pkg: moniker, range
@kitz/monorepo: pnpm

Some nested modules (e.g. str/char) may be intentionally omitted if only accessed through parent namespace — needs case-by-case review.
